      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Brussels, 4 May 1887 ¶ Royal Academy of Sciences, ¶ Letters and Beaux-Arts of Belgium ¶ Palace of the Academies ¶ Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">87.05.04a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Jean-Baptiste-Joseph Liagre</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">P87/1748, unit 107, VPRS 1163/P1 inward correspondence files, VA 672 Premier's Office, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.4929in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: end; text-indent: -0.4929in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Bruxelles, le</seg>
               </seg> 4 mai <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">188</seg>
               </seg>7</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">ACADÉMIE ROYALE</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">
                  <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">des</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">
                  <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">sciences, des lettres et des beaux-arts</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">
                  <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>de belgique</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; ">
                  <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">Palais des Académies</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Monsieur,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>La Bibliothèque de l'Académie vous saura gré de bien vouloir lui compléter la liste de vos ouvrages. A cette fin — conformément à votre lettre du 25 mars — je vous transcris ci-après les titres de ceux de vous ouvrages dont je suis déjà en possession.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Veuillez agréer, Monsieur, l'expression de mes sentiments les plus distingués.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Le Secrétaire perpétuel</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. Liagre</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Monsieur le baron F. von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">botaniste du Gouvernement à Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Descript. and illustr. of the Myoporinous plants II</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">The plants indigenous around Sharks Bay …</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Select extra-tropical plants readily eligible for industrial culture …</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>— new edit.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Index perfectus ad Caroli Linnaei species plantarum …</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Notes on a new proteaceous tree.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Systematic census of australian plants … part 1</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Observations on new vegetable fossils of the auriferous drift.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Census of the genera of plants … indigenous to Australia</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Reports of the mining surveyors and registrars, quarter ended 31 march 1882.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS accompanied by a printed list, presumably taken from a general catalogue of publications, of seven of M's works, numbered 3777 to 3783, namely <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Fragmenta</seg>, 11 vols; <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Plants indigenous to the colony of Victoria</seg>, 2 vols (Thalamiflorae, Lithograms); <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Vegetation of the Chatham Islands</seg>; <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Analytical drawings of Australian mosses</seg>; <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select plants</seg> (1876 ed.); <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Native plants of Victoria</seg>; <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Eucalyptographia</seg>, Decades 1-4, 6,7. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M forwarded Liagre's letter to the Acting Chief Secretary; see M to C. Pearson, 7 June 1887 (in this edition as 87-06-07a). From there it was forwarded to the Premier's Office on 10 June 1887, and ultimately to the Government Printer and the Librarian, Public Library, who was instructed 'to ask for exchange', 12 August 1887<seg style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Brussels, 4 May 1887</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Royal Academy of Sciences,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Letters and Beaux-Arts of Belgium</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Palace of the Academies</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Library of the Academy would be grateful if you would be kind enough to complete its holding of your works. To this end — in accordance with your letter of 5 March<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> — I set out below the titles of those of your works that I already have.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See the list above.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With the deepest respect,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. Liagre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Permanent Secretary</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron F. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, ﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽﷽; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist at Melbourne.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
